definition.ISO:639:3:eng: The name of the administrator user.
The password of the administrator user.
description.ISO:639:3:eng: Provide a password for the user.

definition.ISO:639:3:eng: The e-mail address of the user.
description.ISO:639:3:eng: Provide the e-mail address of the user.
note.ISO:639:3:eng: This address will be used to communicate with the user.

description.ISO:639:3:eng: Select the preferred language of the user.
note.ISO:639:3:eng: User interface elements that are stored in different languages will be displayed in this language, if avaliable.

description.ISO:639:3:eng: The code used to log in.
note.ISO:639:3:eng: If omitted, it will automatically set to the user’s e-mail address.

description.ISO:639:3:eng: The language code of the user’s preferred language.
note.ISO:639:3:eng: If omitted, it will be set to the default application language.

description.ISO:639:3:eng: The group to which the user belongs.
The preferred language of the user.
